One option for vaccination of raccoons has not been approached in
this string, My question is why not feed the raccoon the oral
vaccine which is being used for aerial drops to vaccinate coyotes? I
will admit that we have vaccinated more fire ants than we have coyotes.
However, the raccoons in question are in captivity.
N.C. Ronald PhD
Texas Vet. Med. Diag. Lab
